      <title>交易商关注冬季风险，欧洲天然气停止抛售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/european-gas-prices-approach-oversold-zone-after-three-day-selloff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易商权衡近期充足的供应与冬季风险，欧洲天然气价格上涨，停止了跌入超卖区域的趋势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/european-gas-prices-approach-oversold-zone-after-three-day-selloff</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 06:46:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
